WEBVTT

00:01.787 --> 00:02.985
There was a woman.

00:03.022 --> 00:05.422
She lived in this car with a kid.

00:05.458 --> 00:07.224
She got me into some
small-time robberies

00:07.259 --> 00:09.393
to pay for the drugs.

00:09.428 --> 00:13.163
The reason I stayed was
because of that kid.

00:13.199 --> 00:15.165
I called her Smurf.

00:15.609 --> 00:17.542
BAZ: My mark knows the ins
and outs of the base.

00:17.577 --> 00:19.444
- Wait, your mark?
- Yeah, Paul.

00:19.479 --> 00:20.745
(GLASS BREAKS)

00:20.781 --> 00:24.182
There is a ton of cash on that base.

00:24.217 --> 00:26.117
DERAN: This is a big job.

00:26.153 --> 00:28.653
We're taking a lot of risks.

00:28.688 --> 00:30.722
(LIQUID BUBBLING)

00:30.757 --> 00:32.457
SMURF: What's your name, dude?

00:32.491 --> 00:34.092
I'm Vin.

00:34.127 --> 00:35.994
POPE: Did you see Lucy
while you were there?

00:36.029 --> 00:37.029
How's Cath?

00:37.548 --> 00:40.623
SMURF: I hadn't seen Cath in
weeks, and then she shows up,

00:40.648 --> 00:44.024
steals 10 grand from behind
the dryer, and disappears.

00:44.150 --> 00:47.985
SMURF: She's betrayed you over and over,

00:48.020 --> 00:51.055
and now she's betraying your family.

00:51.090 --> 00:54.858
Are you asking me to sleep
with a 17-year-old kid?

00:54.894 --> 00:57.394
Of course not. That would be illegal.

00:58.595 --> 01:00.428
Alexa tells me you
have reason to believe

01:00.464 --> 01:02.664
your grandmother and your uncles
might be planning another crime.

01:02.699 --> 01:05.233
You're gonna put on that wire,
find out what they're planning,

01:05.269 --> 01:08.537
when they're planning to do it,
and we're gonna take 'em down.

01:08.572 --> 01:09.671
No.

01:09.706 --> 01:10.805
♪

01:10.841 --> 01:12.707
Baz isn't back yet.

01:13.710 --> 01:15.076
You're in danger.

01:15.112 --> 01:17.078
Excuse me.

