23:43.670 --> 23:45.091
(GRUNTING)

23:45.123 --> 23:45.889
Wake up.

23:45.924 --> 23:47.624
Wake up. Look at me.

23:47.659 --> 23:49.759
You with me? You with me?

23:49.794 --> 23:52.929
Hey, wake up. Look at me.
