23:52.964 --> 23:55.064
Look at me. Look at me.

23:55.100 --> 23:57.033
You told Smurf you were
going to take her.

23:57.068 --> 23:59.302
You said it. You remember saying it?

23:59.337 --> 24:01.237
You said it.

24:02.908 --> 24:04.340
People say a lot of things.

24:04.376 --> 24:05.174
Yeah?

24:05.210 --> 24:07.677
Don't follow through.

24:09.748 --> 24:11.581
You tried to rape her
and she fought back?

24:11.616 --> 24:12.782
Look at me, you piece of shit.

24:12.817 --> 24:14.584
